<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Features - Bonded</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: whitesmoke;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            color: #444;
            line-height: 1.8;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        footer {
            position: relative;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        
        }

        .content-container {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .text {
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 50%;
            padding: 20px;
        }

            .text h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
                color: #333;
                font-weight: 600;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .text p {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }

        .image {
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 50%;
            padding: 20px;
        }

            .image img {
                width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                border-radius: 12px;
                box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            }

        .image-right {
            order: 1;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="content-container">
        <!-- First Section: Creating Profiles, Liking Posts, and Following Others -->
        <div class="section">
            <div class="text">
                <h2>Create Profiles, Like Posts, and Follow Others</h2>
                <p>
                    Bonded gives you the power to create a personalized profile that showcases who you are. Share your experiences, passions, and achievements with the world. You can like posts, engage with content, and follow others who share similar interests to stay updated with their latest activities.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Create connections and engage with others by liking posts, following users, and sharing your own content. Whether you're looking to make friends or grow professionally, Bonded offers a space where you can interact meaningfully.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="image">
                <img src="~/images/9.png" alt="Create Profile">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Second Section: Chat with People and Connect -->
        <div class="section">
            <div class="text image-right">
                <h2>Chat with People and Connect</h2>
                <p>
                    Bonded allows you to directly connect with individuals from all around the globe. Whether you're chatting with friends, business contacts, or like-minded individuals, our chat feature makes communication easy and seamless. Send instant messages, share ideas, and strengthen your network.
                </p>
                <p>
                    The platform is designed to help you build lasting relationships by connecting you with others. Share knowledge, insights, and experiences through private messages or group chats.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="image">
                <img src="~/images/10.png" alt="Chat and Connect">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Third Section: Commenting on Posts -->
        <div class="section">
            <div class="text">
                <h2>Comment on Posts</h2>
                <p>
                    Engage with the Bonded community by commenting on posts. Share your thoughts, ask questions, or provide feedback. Commenting allows for deeper interactions with others' content and fosters a dynamic conversation environment.
                </p>
                <p>
                    You can participate in discussions, offer advice, or simply share your opinion. Commenting on posts is an easy way to contribute to the community and make your voice heard.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="image">
                <img src="~/images/11.png" alt="Comment on Posts">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
